---
import Icon from './Icons.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Healthcare Leaders Say</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Join dozens of facilities that trust MedGuard for their generator compliance
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">
          "MedGuard saved us during our AHCA inspection. Their digital portal had every document the inspector needed, organized and ready. We passed with zero citations for the first time in years."
        </p>
        <div class="border-t pt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold">Sarah Martinez</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Administrator, Sunset Gardens ALF</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">
          "When Hurricane Ian hit, MedGuard was here within 2 hours to ensure our generators kept running. They understand that for us, power isn't just convenience - it's life or death."
        </p>
        <div class="border-t pt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold">Dr. James Chen</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Medical Director, Broward Care Center</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1">
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
            <Icon name="star" size={20} class="text-yellow-400" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">
          "The bilingual team is a game-changer. My maintenance staff can actually communicate with the technicians. Plus, their compliance guarantee gives me peace of mind."
        </p>
        <div class="border-t pt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold">Roberto Diaz</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Facilities Manager, Miami Medical Plaza</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust Indicators -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">50+</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Healthcare Facilities Served</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">100%</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">AHCA Inspection Pass Rate</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">4hr</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Average Emergency Response</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600">24/7</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Support Available</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>